dct_title_s: Almaty iInformative guide : where to stay, where to go, where relaxe...
dct_description_sm: Map shows city districts by color coding; railway and bus terminals; subway stations and lines; roads; airports; places of worship. Ancillary map on verso: Almaty tourist region. Includes index of street names, and tourist information.
